author: Shanyce
title: Shanyce
text: We loved using Taxi Box! We had a few complications with our settlement date therefore we had to make so many changes to our Taxi Box plans however the staff were so helpful and accommodating! We wanted a professional company who we could trust with basically our whole house worth of furniture and they met all of our expectations!
